s a Public Health problem. Important regional variations, not well understood yet, and several risk factors were found, which makes us wonder: is there only one or many asthmas in Brazil?",Journal Article||Review,,S0103-05822014000100114 [pii]||10.1590/s0103-05822014000100018 [doi],NLM,19840462
